    <div class="module_container module_container--outer">
        
       
        <div class="module_container module_container--inner">
            <h2 class="module-details_title">
                <span id="_ctrl0_ctl39_lblModuleDetailHeadline">Altria Reports 2021 Third-Quarter and Nine-Months Results; Announces Expanded Share Repurchase Program; Narrows 2021 Full-Year Earnings Guidance</span>
            </h2>
            <div class="module_container module_container--content">
                <div class="module_date-time">
                    <span id="_ctrl0_ctl39_lblDate" class="module_date-text">10/28/2021</span>
                </div>
                <div class="module_links module_q4-icon-links">
                    <div class="module_related-document">
                        <a href="//s204.q4cdn.com/505541855/files/doc_financials/2021/q3/Press-Release.pdf" id="_ctrl0_ctl39_hrefDownload" class="module_link module_news-details_download" target="_blank">
                            <span id="_ctrl0_ctl39_lblDownload" class="module_link-text">Download this Press Release</span>
                            <span class="sr-only">PDF Format (opens in new window)</span>
                            <span id="_ctrl0_ctl39_lblDocument" class="module_file-size">PDF 363 KB</span>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <div id="_ctrl0_ctl39_ulAttachments" class="module_attachments">
                        
                                
                                <a href="https://services.choruscall.com/links/mo211028.html" id="_ctrl0_ctl39_rptAttachments_ctl00_hrefOnline" target="_blank" class="module_link">Webcast</a>
                            
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="module_body">
                    <style type="text/css">.q4default .bwalignc { text-align: center; list-style-position: inside }.q4default .bwalignl { text-align: left }.q4default .bwalignr { text-align: right; list-style-position: inside }.q4default .bwblockalignl { margin-left: 0px; margin-right: auto }.q4default .bwcellpmargin { margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px }.q4default .bwdoublebottom { border-bottom: double black 2.25pt }.q4default .bwleftsingle { border-left: solid black 1pt }.q4default .bwlistcircle { list-style-type: circle }.q4default .bwlistdisc { list-style-type: disc }.q4default .bwpadl0 { padding-left: 0px }.q4default .bwpadl2 { padding-left: 10px }.q4default .bwpadl4 { padding-left: 20px }.q4default .bwpadr0 { padding-right: 0px }.q4default .bwrightsingle { border-right: solid black 1pt }.q4default .bwrowaltcolor0 { background-color: #cceeff }.q4default .bwsinglebottom { border-bottom: solid black 1pt }.q4default .bwtablemarginb { margin-bottom: 10px }.q4default .bwtopsingle { border-top: solid black 1pt }.q4default .bwuline { text-decoration: underline }.q4default .bwvertalignb { vertical-align: bottom }.q4default .bwwidth1 { width: 1% }.q4default .bwwidth10 { width: 10% }.q4default .bwwidth100 { width: 100% }.q4default .bwwidth11 { width: 11% }.q4default .bwwidth12 { width: 12% }.q4default .bwwidth18 { width: 18% }.q4default .bwwidth2 { width: 2% }.q4default .bwwidth20 { width: 20% }.q4default .bwwidth21 { width: 21% }.q4default .bwwidth23 { width: 23% }.q4default .bwwidth24 { width: 24% }.q4default .bwwidth28 { width: 28% }.q4default .bwwidth3 { width: 3% }.q4default .bwwidth30 { width: 30% }.q4default .bwwidth34 { width: 34% }.q4default .bwwidth37 { width: 37% }.q4default .bwwidth39 { width: 39% }.q4default .bwwidth4 { width: 4% }.q4default .bwwidth45 { width: 45% }.q4default .bwwidth48 { width: 48% }.q4default .bwwidth49 { width: 49% }.q4default .bwwidth5 { width: 5% }.q4default .bwwidth51 { width: 51% }.q4default .bwwidth54 { width: 54% }.q4default .bwwidth56 { width: 56% }.q4default .bwwidth58 { width: 58% }.q4default .bwwidth6 { width: 6% }.q4default .bwwidth61 { width: 61% }.q4default .bwwidth63 { width: 63% }.q4default .bwwidth66 { width: 66% }.q4default .bwwidth7 { width: 7% }.q4default .bwwidth73 { width: 73% }.q4default .bwwidth74 { width: 74% }.q4default .bwwidth76 { width: 76% }.q4default .bwwidth8 { width: 8% }.q4default .bwwidth9 { width: 9% }</style><div class="q4default"><p>    RICHMOND, Va.--(BUSINESS WIRE)--
Altria Group, Inc. (Altria) (NYSE: MO) today reports its 2021 third-quarter and nine-months business results, announces the expansion of its existing share repurchase program and narrows its 2021 full-year adjusted diluted earnings per share (EPS) guidance.
</p><p>
“Altria continued to balance maximizing profitability from our core tobacco businesses with investing to realize our Vision of responsibly leading the transition of adult smokers to a smoke-free future,” said Billy Gifford, Altria’s Chief Executive Officer. “Our tobacco businesses performed well against difficult year-over-year comparisons and we’re encouraged by the significant retail share growth from <i>on! </i>in the third quarter. We also continued to reward shareholders with a strong and growing dividend and announced today the expansion of our existing $2.0 billion share repurchase program to $3.5 billion.”
</p><p>
“We are raising the lower-end of our full-year 2021 guidance and now expect to deliver adjusted diluted EPS in a range of $4.58 to $4.62. This range represents a growth rate of 5% to 6% from a $4.36 base in 2020.”
</p><p>
